Package org.eclipse.gef.mvc.fx.models

Class SnappingModel

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.gef.mvc.fx.models.SnappingModel
public class SnappingModel extends Object
The SnappingModel stores SnappingModel.SnappingLocations for which feedback is generated by the SnappingBehavior.
